en v&acirc;n đen xuy&ecirc;n th&acirc;́u đ&acirc;̀y &acirc;́n tượng. Đ&acirc;́y là chưa k&ecirc;̉ đ&ecirc;́n bao nhi&ecirc;u ánh nhìn ghen tị của những c&ocirc; gái khác.&nbsp; <strong>Christian Louboutin</strong> đảm bảo thoả mãn mong ước th&acirc;̀m kín, tăng đ&ocirc;̣ nóng cho chính bạn với item chưa h&ecirc;̀ hạ nhi&ecirc;̣t trong b&ocirc;̣ sưu t&acirc;̣p xu&acirc;n hè&nbsp; 2014 này .&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Gi&aacute;: <em>Từ&nbsp;VND 19,380,000++</em></p>',NULL),(367,182,'en','Charmed ','charmed','<p>Whatever statement you want to make, Pandora presence is to record those special moments.</p>','<p>Did you know charm bracelets were renowned during Victorian time, but literally fell out of style? Until <strong>Pandora</strong> brought it back to life, and made it popular ever again since 2000. Even the brand already started their business in Denmark back in the 80s, and sold other types of jewelry including rings, earrings, necklaces, and watches.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Whatever statement you want to make, <strong>Pandora</strong> presence is to record those special moments with a wealthy closet full of beautiful add-on charms, in which the label is well known for. And their charm bracelets are made of sterling silver &ndash; 92.5% pure silver to ensure its long lasting life.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For this coming Mother&rsquo;s day, let us introduce this graceful gift set you cannot miss. The set comprises of a charm bracelet, a pair of earrings, and a matching ring. So instead of sending a note card to your mom, get this set checked to commemorate the &ldquo;sweet mother&rdquo; moment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Price :&nbsp;From VND 1,180,000 ++</em></p>',NULL),(368,182,'vi','Ngày Của Mẹ ','ngay-cua-me','<p>B&acirc;́t kì khoảnh khắc đáng nhớ nào trong cu&ocirc;̣c s&ocirc;́ng, Pandora sẽ lu&ocirc;n ở đó đ&ecirc;̉ ghi nhớ chúng cùng với bạn.</p>','<p>Vòng tay n&agrave;y r&acirc;́t